properties.headline: FLOODING - BOGGABRI TO GUNNEDAH Kamilaroi Highway
properties.otherAdvice: Several other local roads in the area may be closed or affected by flooding. Please visit the Gunnedah Shire Council website for current conditions on local roads.
properties.diversions:
All vehicles can use the following alternative route, via Coonabarabran.

Southbound: Newell Hwy then Oxley Hwy.
Northbound: Oxley Hwy then Newell Hwy.

Heavy vehicles will continue to use the Bloomfield St bypass to access the Oxley Hwy diversion.

properties.headline: FLOODING - WEE WAA TO NARRABRI Kamilaroi Highway between Purcell Avenue AND Newell Highway
properties.adviceB: Allow extra travel time; 	Never drive through floodwater
properties.diversions:
Eastbound: From Walgett; Gwydir Hwy to Moree and Newell Hwy to Narrabri.
Westbound: Newell Hwy to Moree and Gwydir Hwy to Walgett.

These diversions are suitable for all vehicles.

There is a load limit on the Grawan Creek Bridge east of Collarenebri. Traffic controllers are on site restricting heavy vehicles to one vehicle over the bridge at a time to allow all vehicles to pass.
